channel.title: Stuck and can't jump out [Fixed]
channel.description: There is a part right at the beginning after the major expolsion.. where you come to a T junction.. computers ahead of you but you need to turn right.. If you head towards the computers and back again.. there is some exposed pipe and the floor has lifted. .. if you fall in there.. no matter how much you jump you can not get out of the hole.
